Mrs Danczuk – who has become well-known for posting revealing pictures of herself on Twitter – claimed she was raped by a family member ‘hundreds of times’ between the ages of six and 12.

She did not name her attacker initially, but Mr Burke was later arrested. Last week he denied the claims, saying: ‘The allegations are false. I’m just so shocked and disgusted by it all.’

